title: to build or run something other than main
pid: 2eacc37a-9f8a-4418-93c3-799939ffcb58
body: |2-
    cargo {run, build} --bin executable-name
    where executable-name is defined in a bin passage,
    for instance
  #+BEGIN_SRC toml
  [[bin]] # more bin sections can be added
  name = "not-main"
  path = "not-main.rs"
  #+END_SRC
